    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/22e6305f97791a7879d7ffa8645be531.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=190 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/fc0084ea8ae1976a72a0bb673eea53ba.poster.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/fc0084ea8ae1976a72a0bb673eea53ba.webm?t=1728635348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/fc0084ea8ae1976a72a0bb673eea53ba.mp4?t=1728635348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《蛋丸之地》初代上架后，得到了很多有价值的反馈。在《蛋丸之地2》中，我结合反馈对玩法进行了升级，进一步强化了策略性与流派的构建，并引入了强大的英灵蛋、更多的新技能与新的敌人形态；在美术效果上，我寻找了一位合作伙伴对美术效果进行了全面优化，让游戏体验更加舒适；在内容上，二代拥有比一代数量更多的全新关卡，每个关卡提供多种困难模式供挑战。希望这些变化能带来更好的游戏体验，也期待收到更多的建议与反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/ad140c53dea06d2fdc38833cc16a91fc.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=315 /></span>《蛋丸之地2》除了能建造1代的6种基础蛋与20种高级蛋外，在地图中还能唤醒6种技能特性不同的英灵蛋。运用英灵蛋们的强大力量巩固战线！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/1eec912779e25ff46fb04673c66c592d.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=315 /></span>每种基础蛋都可以选择四种升级路线，根据地形与怪物特征选择不同的升级路线以挑战更具威胁的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/f37480a10973ec774fa4676bb216982d.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=315 /></span>每种高级蛋可以在6种技能中选择3项进行学习，每种英灵蛋可以在8种技能中选择4项进行学习，在庞大的策略库中选择多种技能搭配，构筑起属于自己的阵容！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/c08512e927966ff1db6d400cecbee9ee.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=315 /></span>在关卡中收集的资源将用于解锁你的科技树，从而在后续的战斗中获得更强大的力量。随着战斗的深入，蛋蛋家族将茁壮成长。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105990/extras/34c697bf70207aa0bfe21e893612f241.avif?t=1728635348\" width=616 height=315 /></span>随着战役波次的深入解锁挑战模式，面对不同的困难挑战，在黑暗森林中开辟出一片属于蛋丸王国的领土！</p>",
